Gerd Sannemüller (19 October 1914, Heilbad Heiligenstadt – 13 June 2008) was a German composer, pianist and musicologist.
In 1961 he received his Doctor of Philosophy degree.
From 1965 to 1983 he served as a professor of musicology and music education in Kiel.
